### API Endpoints
# | Method | Path            | 설명              |
# | POST   | /product        | 상품 등록         |
# | PATCH  | /product/:id    | 상품 수정         |
# | DELETE | /product/:id    | 상품 삭제         |
# | POST   | /order          | 주문 생성         |
# | GET    | /order/my       | 내 주문 내역 조회 |
# | POST   | /payment/verify | 결제 검증         |


### register user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json 

{
    "email": "ggh93@naver.com",
    "password": "qwer1234",
    "name": "테스터"
}

### login user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json  

{
    "email": "ggh93@naver.com",
    "password": "qwer1234"
}

### product list
GET http://localhost:3000/product

### product detail
GET http://localhost:3000/product/3

### create product
POST http://localhost:3000/product
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOjEsImVtYWlsIjoiZ2doOTNAbmF2ZXIuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc2NzYzMDUyLCJleHAiOjE3NzczNjc4NTJ9.pDpoF4jGGS1pi7rEbi7NC2HNUZ7yfWqFh-y7G0klPFU

{
    "name": "나이키 운동화",
    "description": "편안한 착용감과 세련된 디자인의 나이키 운동화입니다.",
    "price": 50000,
    "stock": 10
}

